relevant_findings.general: Alert and oriented x 3, no acute distress, pleasant.
relevant_findings.HEENT: No scleral icterus, mucous membranes moist, atraumatic/normocephalic.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, no murmurs/gallops/rubs.
relevant_findings.pulmonary: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes/rhonchi/crackles, no respiratory distress.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, nondistended, tender to palpation in the lower abdomen especially suprapubic and left lower quadrant, no rebound or guarding, no palpable masses.
relevant_findings.extremities: No edema, warm and well perfused.
